  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 5
  Paragraph: 4
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Ch'ang Chi said, "If he's lost a foot and is still superior to the
Master, then how far above the common run of men he must be! A man like
that - what unique way does he have of using his mind?"
